            ],
            "parameters": {
                "color": 7,
                "width": 814,
                "height": 1096,
                "content": "## Priority Matrix\n\nBuilds a detailed context matrix linking each priority to its relevant signals, emails, and decisions. Deduplicates and normalizes the data."
